* {{ill|Michikaeshi no Ōkami|ja|道反大神|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Michikaeshi no Ōkami|qq=}}
* {{ill|Shinatsuhiko|ja|国御柱命|lt=Kuni no Mihashira no Mikoto|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinatsuhiko|qq=}}

